data.text:
Are you ready to take your game room to the next level with the NHL Licensed Super Chexx Pro Bubble Hockey? This ultimate arcade game features all-new live action game calls and videos, allowing you to immerse yourself in the thrill of the game like never before. With the ability to choose your away and home team, you can recreate your favorite matchups right in your own home.

Picture does not change with selected configurations; your base will have the home and away team logos based on home and away team selections.
